snippet.title: RevenBlade - Gameplay Announce Trailer (2023)
snippet.description:
It's time to sharpen your blades. Wishlist on Steam now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2247220/RevenBlade/

RevenBlade is team-based third-person hero shooter with MOBA elements and a focus on melee combat with fast-paced action and mechanical outplays.

Join the Discord Community: http://Discord.gg/XtMN6Ft
Follow Us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/RevenBlade
Website: https://www.revenblade.com/
